column1: Data description: CV of cover for 41 generalists species
Names of data takers: Calculated by Barbara Fernandez-Going
Column info: Species, site (1-80), soil type, and CV of cover (cover was averaged over quadrats, for a single value per site per year, then the CV of years was calculated)
Definitions & Abbreviations: S=Serpentine, N=Non-serpentine, CV=coefficient of variation
